<br>
IMHO Wizards are vital for almost every single encounter in the game.  No matter what encounter it is, Wizards will always have a use.<br>
<br>
For those of you who disagree with Wizards + Velious = Good, you're wrong.  Wizards ARE needed for every single Velious encounter.  There have been times when we first went up against mobs where a few lone Wizards left behind saved the day and the mob fell.  Even in these 150k+ mob fights, Wizards can easily contribute 6-8K even 10k if we really try hard (mod robes / mana robes).  <br>
<br>
When you go up against a Velious mob that is Bane-enabled we deal THE most damage by at least 5k in most situations.  Never underestimate the power of these two spells, the own.<br>
<br>
When you take us back to Kunark and the old world, we rock vs. 32k mobs.  I remember when Trak was first being attempted and a big factor that could help you win was the number of Wizards you had there!<br>
<br>
Yes, I will be the first one to say that we are not 100% perfect, but I will be the very last to say we suck and we are broke.  I think Grim put it nicely. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
